    "en": {
      "title": "Harin - Manusha who renounced ministerial posts",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Manusha Nanayakkara and Harin Fernando have announced that they will resign from their ministerial posts with effect.",
        "In a statement, they announced that they have taken this decision with the aim of forming an all-party government and providing relief to the people. (a)"
      ],
